data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT - Renovation and extension in 1999.  Architect drawings available at the property.  Ceilings raised in living and dining rooms, dining room enlarged.  Kitchen gutted, redesigned with new cabinets, double ovens. Laundry now pantry with original kitchen cabinets and sink.  Extended back of house, large master and new full bath with separate shower and jacuzzi tub. Family room with built-ins.  Wide stair case to downstairs private office/4th bedroom/hobby room.  Easy walkup staircase to floored attic.  Recent  roof, Bruce hardwood flooring 2 yrs. Tremendous storage/closets. Large fenced yard with deck and view of Green Mountain.  Walk to YMCA, Bank, Grocery store/ Greenway
